=\"/wiki/Proto-Australoid\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Proto-Australoid\">Proto-Australoid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ancestral_South_Indian\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ancestral South Indian\">Ancestral South Indian</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Proto-Mongoloid\" title=\"Proto-Mongoloid\">Proto-Mongoloid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ancient_North_Eurasian\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ancient North Eurasian\">Ancient North Eurasian</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/European_early_modern_humans\" title=\"European early modern humans\">Early Modern European</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Ancestral_Native_American\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ancestral Native American\">Ancestral Native American</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Sons_of_Noah\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sons of Noah\">Noahide</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Semitic_people\" title=\"Semitic people\">Semitic</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Hamitic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hamitic\">Hamitic</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Japhetites\" title=\"Japhetites\">Japhetic</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"width:1%\"><a href=\"/wiki/Sociology_of_race_and_ethnic_relations\" title=\"Sociology of race and ethnic relations\">Sociological</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-even hlist\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li>By region\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Historical_definitions_of_races_in_India\" title=\"Historical definitions of races in India\">in India</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Race_and_ethnicity_in_Latin_America\" title=\"Race and ethnicity in Latin America\">in Latin America</a>\n<ul><li><a 